Dialogue: 0,0:48:19.37,0:48:22.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听到你的歌 大家一定会非常惊叹
Dialogue: 0,0:48:23.56,0:48:28.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我考虑了一下这件事
Dialogue: 0,0:48:29.41,0:48:34.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在你唱歌时 我会悄悄守在一旁
Dialogue: 0,0:48:35.80,0:48:37.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,简直像做梦般
Dialogue: 0,0:48:37.73,0:48:39.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是梦
Dialogue: 0,0:48:39.64,0:48:41.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梦总会变成现实的
Dialogue: 0,0:48:42.26,0:48:44.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克莉斯汀・黛那
Dialogue: 0,0:48:44.48,0:48:49.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上帝正微笑着\N你的梦想要成真了
Dialogue: 0,0:49:00.52,0:49:02.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 换你了
Dialogue: 0,0:49:31.81,0:49:38.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔 you are music
Dialogue: 0,0:49:38.85,0:49:49.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的歌声宛如温柔的天使之音
Dialogue: 0,0:49:53.36,0:49:57.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔 you are music
Dialogue: 0,0:49:58.00,0:50:12.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的歌声夜夜抚慰着我
Dialogue: 0,0:50:17.46,0:50:27.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我心中的思慕 但愿歌声能传达
