Dialogue: 0,0:51:44.68,0:51:48.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请尽情欢唱
Dialogue: 0,0:51:48.46,0:51:55.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏登伯爵出席的晚宴
Dialogue: 0,0:51:55.41,0:52:01.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请尽情欢享快乐时光吧
Dialogue: 0,0:52:03.83,0:52:04.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,强・库拉多
Dialogue: 0,0:52:04.50,0:52:05.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伯爵有何吩咐
Dialogue: 0,0:52:05.36,0:52:06.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到克莉斯汀了吗
