Dialogue: 0,1:57:09.31,1:57:10.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲利普
Dialogue: 0,1:57:11.52,1:57:13.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救我 菲利普
Dialogue: 0,1:57:13.87,1:57:15.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点
Dialogue: 0,1:57:17.86,1:57:19.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克莉斯汀
Dialogue: 0,1:57:19.91,1:57:21.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来人啊 乔・克鲁德
Dialogue: 0,1:57:21.76,1:57:23.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快来帮忙 克莉斯汀
Dialogue: 0,1:57:25.66,1:57:26.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伯爵
Dialogue: 0,1:57:26.86,1:57:28.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么也打不开 克莉斯汀在里面
Dialogue: 0,1:57:28.47,1:57:29.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是
Dialogue: 0,1:57:32.67,1:57:34.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快让开 我来
Dialogue: 0,1:57:39.01,1:57:39.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲利普
Dialogue: 0,1:57:39.92,1:57:40.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克莉斯汀
Dialogue: 0,1:57:40.82,1:57:42.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出什么事了
Dialogue: 0,1:57:42.99,1:57:47.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看到他的脸了
Dialogue: 0,1:57:47.74,1:57:49.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,1:57:50.03,1:57:53.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快带这孩子离开 快
Dialogue: 0,1:57:54.69,1:57:58.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 都是因为我求他才会这样
Dialogue: 0,1:57:58.75,1:58:01.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以为看到他的脸后不会有什么事
Dialogue: 0,1:58:01.12,1:58:04.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而他也相信我了
Dialogue: 0,1:58:05.81,1:58:07.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我必须回去
Dialogue: 0,1:58:07.66,1:58:09.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我必须见他
Dialogue: 0,1:58:09.11,1:58:11.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 那太危险了
Dialogue: 0,1:58:11.06,1:58:12.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快带她走
Dialogue: 0,1:58:12.46,1:58:13.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克莉斯汀
Dialogue: 0,1:58:13.20,1:58:15.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快走 大家都离开这儿
Dialogue: 0,1:58:15.30,1:58:16.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,1:58:42.87,1:58:46.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幽…幽灵
Dialogue: 0,1:58:58.24,1:58:59.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,1:58:59.12,1:59:00.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个家伙出现了
Dialogue: 0,1:59:00.37,1:59:01.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就让他从眼前逃了吗
Dialogue: 0,1:59:01.75,1:59:02.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,1:59:02.77,1:59:04.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙肯定向屋顶那儿逃了
Dialogue: 0,1:59:04.28,1:59:05.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听好了 把他找出来
Dialogue: 0,1:59:05.98,1:59:06.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,1:59:07.43,1:59:09.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡洛塔她…
Dialogue: 0,1:59:09.28,1:59:12.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我妻子…被谋杀了
Dialogue: 0,1:59:12.33,1:59:13.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,1:59:15.05,1:59:17.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 快点去搜啊
Dialogue: 0,1:59:30.55,1:59:31.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快看 有血迹
Dialogue: 0,1:59:31.78,1:59:32.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他肯定来过这儿
Dialogue: 0,1:59:32.89,1:59:34.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙一定就在附近
Dialogue: 0,1:59:35.54,1:59:36.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那好…
Dialogue: 0,1:59:36.74,1:59:38.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仔细搜索这附近
Dialogue: 0,1:59:38.22,1:59:40.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一带我来找吧
Dialogue: 0,1:59:41.22,1:59:43.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,道具房还是我比较熟悉
Dialogue: 0,1:59:43.57,1:59:45.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们去搜其他地方
Dialogue: 0,1:59:45.96,1:59:48.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 小心了
Dialogue: 0,2:00:02.03,2:00:03.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾瑞克
Dialogue: 0,2:00:11.39,2:00:13.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没什么关系
Dialogue: 0,2:00:15.61,2:00:18.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把我送回地底去
Dialogue: 0,2:00:18.14,2:00:19.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,2:00:19.33,2:00:20.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在还不行
Dialogue: 0,2:00:20.56,2:00:22.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地底已经布满了警察
Dialogue: 0,2:00:22.37,2:00:23.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,2:00:26.07,2:00:27.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事
Dialogue: 0,2:00:29.87,2:00:36.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前是我不好
Dialogue: 0,2:00:37.97,2:00:40.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不该对你发火
Dialogue: 0,2:00:41.62,2:00:43.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系的
Dialogue: 0,2:00:45.48,2:00:48.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活着真好啊
Dialogue: 0,2:00:48.58,2:00:51.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我之所以来到这世上
Dialogue: 0,2:00:53.37,2:00:56.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是为了聆听音乐
Dialogue: 0,2:00:58.23,2:00:59.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也这样想
Dialogue: 0,2:01:03.01,2:01:06.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有就是为了聆听克莉斯汀的声音
Dialogue: 0,2:01:06.92,2:01:11.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可她伤害了你
Dialogue: 0,2:01:13.28,2:01:15.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能理解
Dialogue: 0,2:01:16.51,2:01:20.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实是我不好 是我吓到她了
Dialogue: 0,2:01:22.42,2:01:24.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是她的错
Dialogue: 0,2:01:28.84,2:01:32.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她以为自己爱上我了
Dialogue: 0,2:01:34.04,2:01:38.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她即使现在还爱你
Dialogue: 0,2:01:41.06,2:01:43.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经是过去的事了
Dialogue: 0,2:01:44.71,2:01:47.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且也只是一瞬间而已
Dialogue: 0,2:01:48.25,2:01:50.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过这样也没什么不好
Dialogue: 0,2:01:51.16,2:01:54.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要有那一瞬间 我就能活下去了
Dialogue: 0,2:01:55.29,2:02:00.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这其实也很好
Dialogue: 0,2:02:02.34,2:02:05.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,厌恶才能与我这张丑陋的脸相称
Dialogue: 0,2:02:07.04,2:02:08.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过来
Dialogue: 0,2:02:09.35,2:02:10.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来
Dialogue: 0,2:02:31.20,2:02:32.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,2:02:51.04,2:02:53.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一定想看吧
Dialogue: 0,2:02:55.31,2:02:57.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的脸
Dialogue: 0,2:03:00.29,2:03:03.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经看过了
Dialogue: 0,2:03:03.73,2:03:06.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在你小的时候
Dialogue: 0,2:03:11.30,2:03:13.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我小的时候
Dialogue: 0,2:03:18.81,2:03:22.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很了解我母亲吧
Dialogue: 0,2:03:24.35,2:03:25.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,2:03:31.57,2:03:33.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你爱她吗
Dialogue: 0,2:03:35.87,2:03:37.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,2:03:39.86,2:03:43.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么是我母亲让你看我的脸吧
Dialogue: 0,2:03:46.39,2:03:52.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你母亲觉得你的脸非常漂亮
Dialogue: 0,2:03:54.10,2:03:57.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道母亲确实是这样想的
Dialogue: 0,2:03:59.15,2:04:00.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,2:04:01.93,2:04:04.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的眼前浮现着妈妈的面容
Dialogue: 0,2:04:07.19,2:04:08.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾瑞克
Dialogue: 0,2:04:08.66,2:04:13.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我心爱的孩子
Dialogue: 0,2:04:13.74,2:04:19.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是任何人也无法替代的宝物
Dialogue: 0,2:04:19.32,2:04:30.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从你出生开始我便一直守护着你
Dialogue: 0,2:04:30.26,2:04:41.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直坚信 你就是我的父亲
Dialogue: 0,2:04:41.16,2:04:49.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凝视着你那和我相似的眼睛
Dialogue: 0,2:04:52.81,2:05:03.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真想对你说声谢谢
Dialogue: 0,2:05:03.58,2:05:15.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真想喊你一声父亲
Dialogue: 0,2:05:19.86,2:05:21.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾瑞克
Dialogue: 0,2:05:24.34,2:05:36.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么都无法割断父子间的血脉
Dialogue: 0,2:05:36.34,2:05:46.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,音乐将你我紧紧连在一起
Dialogue: 0,2:05:46.26,2:05:59.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾瑞克 你就是我活着的意义
Dialogue: 0,2:06:02.10,2:06:04.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么你怎么想呢
Dialogue: 0,2:06:05.91,2:06:07.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想什么
Dialogue: 0,2:06:09.41,2:06:12.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是自己的孩子的脸啊
Dialogue: 0,2:06:14.32,2:06:17.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世上再也没有比这更可爱的了
Dialogue: 0,2:06:23.85,2:06:27.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还记得我第一次\N在水边看到自己的脸时的事吗
Dialogue: 0,2:06:28.48,2:06:29.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,2:06:30.66,2:06:36.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当时我还以为自己看到的是水怪
Dialogue: 0,2:06:37.02,2:06:38.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊
Dialogue: 0,2:06:39.37,2:06:42.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时间过的真快啊
Dialogue: 0,2:06:42.05,2:06:46.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切都像梦一样
Dialogue: 0,2:06:47.23,2:06:52.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是这样想的啊
Dialogue: 0,2:06:52.31,2:06:57.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而我的这张脸 还是过去的那张脸
Dialogue: 0,2:06:58.58,2:07:00.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是你却成了音乐家
Dialogue: 0,2:07:01.24,2:07:03.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是这样好吗
Dialogue: 0,2:07:04.83,2:07:06.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,2:07:07.11,2:07:12.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你成为了一个优秀的音乐家
Dialogue: 0,2:07:15.60,2:07:27.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直都渴望能在你的怀里安眠
Dialogue: 0,2:07:28.03,2:07:38.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的愿望一定能实现
Dialogue: 0,2:07:38.46,2:07:41.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾瑞克 你就是…
Dialogue: 0,2:07:41.32,2:07:43.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不必说出来
Dialogue: 0,2:07:43.63,2:07:46.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你永远是…
Dialogue: 0,2:07:46.18,2:07:48.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道的
Dialogue: 0,2:07:48.82,2:08:06.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾瑞克 你就是我心爱的儿子
Dialogue: 0,2:08:22.98,2:08:27.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我带你走吧
