Dialogue: 0,2:09:51.11,2:09:52.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求求你
Dialogue: 0,2:10:02.84,2:10:05.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别伤害他 求求你们
Dialogue: 0,2:10:05.29,2:10:07.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求求你们放过他吧
