Dialogue: 0,2:10:09.39,2:10:11.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从四面包围他
Dialogue: 0,2:10:11.87,2:10:16.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙不是人类 要活捉他
Dialogue: 0,2:10:17.02,2:10:18.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上啊
Dialogue: 0,2:10:18.49,2:10:20.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活捉
