Dialogue: 0,2:12:03.94,2:12:07.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托大家都离开吧
Dialogue: 0,2:12:09.86,2:12:14.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托 求求你们
